Brad Oscar https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brad_Oscar 0 Brad Oscar (born September 22, 1964) is an American musical theatre actor, known for his Broadway performances in musicals such as The Producers and Jekyll and Hyde. He has earned two Tony Award nominations; one for The Producers as Franz Liebkind, and one for Something Rotten! as Nostradamus.
